Running this example
====================

1.  Open a console.

2.  Run

        gem bundle

3.  Open a console.

4.  Run

        rackup rubycas_server.ru

5.  Open a console.

6.  Run

        rackup cas_proxy_callback.ru

7.  Open a console.

8.  Run

        rackup fortune_server.ru

9.  Open a console.

10. Run

        ruby fortune_client.rb

11. Open a Web browser.

12. Go to 
      
        http://localhost:4567

13. Enter the login details

        mr296 / br0wn

14. Log in.

15. Play around.
